data.description: Come and Explore this pristine 3 bedroom 2 bath pool home with beautiful vinyl wood plank flooring throughout the entire home.  Smart switches brighten the bathrooms and a spacious pantry compliments the dining room. The master bedroom boasts with a walk in closet.  Best of all, your own personal oasis awaits you beyond the sliding glass doors and within the fenced in yard, showcasing a sparkling pool and gazebo.  Shopping and plenty of eateries are very close with easy access to Maitland exchange, 408 and I-4.  Practical enhancements include an updated HVAC system, electrical wiring, panel and a 2 1/2 year old roof!  This home is the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility.  Make an appointment to view today before it's too late.
